  1→//! Agent persona store for multi-agent support.
  2→//!
  3→//! Each agent has its own workspace directory under `data_dir()/agents/<id>/`
  4→//! with dedicated `IDENTITY.md`, `SOUL.md`, and memory files.
  5→//! The "main" agent uses `data_dir()/agents/main` with fallback reads from the
  6→//! root workspace for backward compatibility.
  7→
  8→use {
  9→    serde::{Deserialize, Serialize},
 10→    std::{
 11→        path::{Path, PathBuf},
 12→        time::{SystemTime, UNIX_EPOCH},
 13→    },
 14→};
